OL,3,C'Don't pick up a weapon', pleads
OL,4,Cmother of teenager killed with machete
OL,6,FThe mother of a 14-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fwas stabbed with a machete has said
OL,8,Fthat carrying weapons destroys lives
OL,9,Fafter two teenagers were found guilty
OL,10,Fof her son's manslaughter.
OL,12,FGordon Gault was stabbed by Carlos
OL,13,FNeto in the Elswick area of Newcastle
OL,14,Fon 9 November 2022 amidst a backdrop
OL,15,Fof 'tit-for-tat' violence between
OL,16,Ffeuding teenage gangs.
OL,18,FHe died in hospital six days later.
