OL,3,C'Don't pick up a weapon', pleads
OL,4,Cmother of teenager killed with machete
OL,6,FNeto, who said he acted in self
OL,7,Fdefence, and friend Lawson Natty, who
OL,8,Fsupplied the machete, were cleared of
OL,9,Fmurder but found guilty of
OL,10,Fmanslaughter at Newcastle Crown Court
OL,11,Fon 15 January.
OL,13,FFour other teenagers were found not
OL,14,Fguilty of murder and acquitted at the
OL,15,Fsame time. Six other youths from
OL,16,Fanother group pleaded guilty to affray
OL,17,Fduring a connected trial.
OL,19,FOn 8 March at the same court, 18-year-
OL,20,Fold Neto was sentenced to nine years
OL,21,Ftwo months for manslaughter.
