OL,6,FNatty, also 18, was sentenced to 32
OL,7,Fmonths for his part in the attack
OL,8,Fwhich saw another boy unlawfully
OL,9,Fwounded.
OL,11,FGordon's mother Dionne Barrett has
OL,12,Fcalled her son's killers sentences "a
OL,13,Fbit disappointing".
OL,15,FOutside of Newcastle Crown Court, she
OL,16,Fsaid: "Neto will be out by the time
OL,17,Fhe's 25. Gordon's not going to have
OL,18,Fthat chance.
