OL,3,C'Don't pick up a weapon', pleads
OL,4,Cmother of teenager killed with machete
OL,6,F"I think it should have been made more
OL,7,Fclear in court that Gordon was never
OL,8,Fever involved in the tit-for-tat
OL,9,Fviolence, Carlos getting stabbed, or
OL,10,Fany of the other fights beforehand.
OL,12,F"Gordon's only involvement was that
OL,13,Fnight and nothing else apart from that.
OL,15,F"Please don't ever ever pick up a
OL,16,Fweapon. It destroys everybody's life."
OL,18,FShe also paid tribute to her son
OL,19,Fsaying: "Gordon lit up the room
OL,20,Feveryday, every time Gordon left the
OL,21,Fhouse he went 'mam I love you'.
