OL,3,C'Don't pick up a weapon', pleads
OL,4,Cmother of teenager killed with machete
OL,6,F"Only two weeks before he died, he met
OL,7,Fa child in care, gave him his money
OL,8,Fbox, his playstation, clothes.
OL,10,F"He was always happy, he was never
OL,11,Fever sad."
OL,13,FFollowing sentencing, Senior
OL,14,FInvestigating Officer Detective Chief
OL,15,FInspector Matt Steel, of Northumbria
OL,16,FPolice, said: "This is an extremely
OL,17,Ftragic case in which a teenager had
OL,18,Fhis future taken away.
