OL,3,C'Don't pick up a weapon', pleads
OL,4,Cmother of teenager killed with machete
OL,6,F"Violence has absolutely no place in
OL,7,Four communities - the impact as we
OL,8,Fhave seen with this case can be
OL,9,Futterly devastating.
OL,11,F"The lives of the two people who have
OL,12,Fbeen jailed for his manslaughter and
OL,13,Fthose who care about them have also
OL,14,Fbeen changed forever by the decisions
OL,15,Fthey made."
OL,17,FHe also called on society to work
OL,18,Ftogether to reduce the impact of knife
OL,19,Fcrime and prevent incidents from
OL,20,Fhappening.
